/* eslint-disable jsx-a11y/anchor-is-valid */
import React, { Component } from "react"
import {
  ProfileWrap,
  Left,
  ListWrap,
  List,
  Link,
  Icon,
  Right,
  Header,
  Title,
  Input,
  Button,
} from "./styles/profile"

import accountIcon from "./img/account.png"
import bookingIcon from "./img/booking.png"
import paymentIcon from "./img/payment.png"
import reviewIcon from "./img/review.png"

class Profile extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <>
        <ProfileWrap>
          <Left>
            <ListWrap>
              <List>
                <Icon src={accountIcon} alt="account" />
                <Link href="#">Profile</Link>
              </List>
              <List>
                <Icon src={bookingIcon} alt="booking" />
                <Link href="#">Bookings</Link>
              </List>
              <List>
                <Icon src={paymentIcon} alt="payment" />
                <Link href="#">Payment</Link>
              </List>
              <List>
                <Icon src={reviewIcon} alt="review" />
                <Link href="#">Reviews</Link>
              </List>
            </ListWrap>
          </Left>
          <Right>
            <Header>Personal Information</Header>
            <Title>First Name</Title>
            <Input type="text" />
            <Title>Last Name</Title>
            <Input type="text" />
            <Title>Email</Title>
            <Input type="email" />
            <Button>Update Profile</Button>
            <Header>Update Password</Header>
            <Title>Current Password</Title>
            <Input type="password" />
            <Title>New Password</Title>
            <Input type="password" />
          </Right>
        </ProfileWrap>
      </>
    )
  }
}
export default Profile
